      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="5396th">5396th meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2006-03-24" refersTo="#adoptionDate">24 March 2006</docDate></docTitle>
